{"tid":1569131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"淘大藍絲事件=誘敵戰 破解? 其實唔難","createTime":"2019-09-14T13:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:40:06.000Z","uid":90601,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd62710ed60b50ad76b31e0e8bee06792ebe364","tid":1569131,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"今日既單野其實可以簡化為「誘敵」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有藍絲出現＞搞事挑釁（撕牆／打人）＞去第二度＞引手足去＞黑警出現＞拉人</strong><br />\n<br />\n同樣操作唔止可以係連儂牆出現<br />\n放映會／人鏈／大合唱活動 都一樣可以出現<br />\n重點就係引你追擊，或即場反擊<br />\n再由黑警／便衣等你落單再拉鳩你<br />\n<br />\n要破解誘敵戰，要記住基本概念：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔夠打唔好打，夠打即場解決，唔好盲追</span></strong><br />\n所以對應方式如下<br />\n<br />\n一、連儂牆加強人手 唔夠打就走<br />\n二、人手充足要解決 5至10分鐘內完事 完事後散 唔好留<br />\n三、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要：</span></strong>唔夠打走就走 唔好跟佢地互鬥/去第二度覆桌，<ins>隨時有埋伏</ins><br />\n<br />\n<em>心理建構：唔好俾對方牽住節奏，連儂牆係死，避走亦唔等於輸，唯一輸既事實=你自己/手足被捕</em>"},{"pid":"1ce60d8294715455912bf56995e0237b3cec92b5","tid":1569131,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45a7ea55853a06c324b812e1f4622a92c03d597d","tid":1569131,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f7373c921a571b09fd6a63b041515d6f50a5f","tid":1569131,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58198b3dfa83253f00b9ae8a07baf56c3842d9bc","tid":1569131,"uid":157938,"like":0,"di